{"tid":2245894,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"世衛發表關於武肺治療藥物的報告","createTime":"2020-10-16T14:51:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T14:59:37.000Z","uid":38861,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"296c36019c8c48058cd2b024cd97ffb2f66754e7","tid":2245894,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T14:51:26.000Z","msg":"早前關於瑞德西韋(Remdesivir)的臨床研究顯示(Ref1)，服用Remdesivir的病人平均康復時間由15日推前為11日，15日的死亡率由11.9%降至7.1%。<br />\n<br />\n而世衛在10月15日發表報告(Ref2,未接受同行評審,non peer-reviewed)，集合30個國家405間醫院的數據，證實瑞德西韋及羥氯喹(hydroxychloroquine)、及其他藥物對武肺病人的死亡率並無任何影響。<br />\n<br />\nY-axis為死亡率，X-axis為住院日數。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M4v3zMs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM4v3zMs.png&h=8f36d2ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRemdesivir：2743人<br />\nControl：2708人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oekSs6v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoekSs6v.png&h=734082a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHydroxychloroquine：947人<br />\nControl：906人<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMoa2007764\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nejm.org%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1056%2FNEJMoa2007764&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVU2CvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=a0dd43ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMoa2007764</a><br />\nRef2:<a href=\"https://www.medrxiv.org/content/10.1101/2020.10.15.20209817v1.full.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.medrxiv.org%2Fcontent%2F10.1101%2F2020.10.15.20209817v1.full.pdf&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVU2CvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=f3fd5246\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.medrxiv.org/content/10.1101/2020.10.15.20209817v1.full.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"ac47ba3d765ec2114b6d1e153dbadce2ea629e23","tid":2245894,"uid":275243,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T14:53:18.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/a